HEADWORD: Breton
<hw>Bret"on</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>breton</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or relating to Brittany, or Bretagne,
in France.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A native or inhabitant of
Brittany, or Bretagne, in France; also, the ancient language of
Brittany; Armorican.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

